msgid "Awards"
msgstr "Subventions"

msgctxt "body.d164c084-e6f3-4602-9b74-4cf6fe76dbe0"
msgid "The Mozilla Technology Fund (MTF) supports open source technologists whose work furthers promising approaches to solving pressing internet health issues."
msgstr ""
"Le Mozilla Technology Fund (MTF) soutient des expert·e·s de l’open source dont les travaux favorisent des approches prometteuses pour résoudre des problèmes urgents relatifs à la santé d’Internet."

msgctxt "body.54588b31-b915-4119-9326-3d0259468170"
msgid "Meet the awardees"
msgstr "Découvrez les lauréats"

msgctxt "body.2002708d-3288-450a-938d-bcdda8e48e89.accordion_items.d960eebf-4ee3-4f49-bb11-a1949762a99d.title"
msgid "2024 Cohort: Open Source AI + Environmental Justice"
msgstr "Cohorte 2024 : IA open source + justice environnementale"

msgctxt "body.2002708d-3288-450a-938d-bcdda8e48e89.accordion_items.d960eebf-4ee3-4f49-bb11-a1949762a99d.content.e5cc1cbb-12e9-473e-9134-6addf1f60932"
msgid "The <a id=\"a1\">newest cohort</a> of the Mozilla Technology Fund will use open-source AI tools to track methane emissions, expose harmful mining operations, monitor air quality, and more."
msgstr ""
"La <a id=\"a1\">nouvelle cohorte</a> du Mozilla Technology Fund utilisera des outils d’IA open source pour pister les émissions de méthane, dénoncer les opérations minières dangereuses, surveiller "
"la qualité de l’air, etc."

